file.name: billing.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Billing API
  license:
    name: Microsoft
paths:
  '/monetizationModels':
    get:
      summary: Gets a list of monetization models for products
      operationId: get_monetization_models
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  result:
                   type: array
                   items:
                    $ref: "#/components/schemas/monetizationModel"
  '/products':
    get:
      summary: Gets a list of APIM products
      operationId: get_products
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  value:
                   type: array
                   items:
                    $ref: "#/components/schemas/product"
components:
  schemas:
    product:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        properties:
          type: object
          properties:
            displayName:
              type: string
            description:
              type: string
            additionalProperties: true
        additionalProperties: true
        
    monetizationModel:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          example: standard
        pricingModelType:
          type: string
          enum:
            - Metered
            - UnitAndMeteredOverage
            - Unit
          example: UnitAndMeteredOverage
        recurring:
          type: object
          properties:
            interval:
              type: string
              enum:
                - day
                - month
                - year
              example: month
            intervalCount:
              type: integer
              example: 1
        prices:
          type: object
          properties:
            unit:
              type: object
              properties:
                currency:
                  type: string
                  example: usd
                unitAmount:
                  type: number
                  example: 89.95
                quota:
                  type: integer
                  example: 50000
                maxUnits:
                  type: integer
                  example: 1
            metered:
              type: object
              properties:
                currency:
                  type: string
                  example: usd
                unitAmount:
                  type: number
                  example: 0.00095
